rComments: Nana teaches anti-colonial studies, this is a revolutionary course and section of education. If you aren't' prepared to do the work required to decolonize your mind, this isn't the class for you. This professor has a RICH knowledge foundation to offer anyone brave enough to come to participate.

Best professor. Not only is Dei a legend in the international community as a anti-racist/colonial scholar. He is compassionate about not only his work, but the work of students. For many, he is the representation we so badly need and want in academia. Dei is a true gem, he created space for PoC to speak of their experiences. Take a course with him
Very disorganized, goes on power trips. Be wary of him. Don't be fooled by the popular name.
